# Messages for BBCode mode
# © StrongED Developers

HlpText:\Sopen a menu with text style options.|MChoose one of the menu items to apply a style to the selected text.
HlpLists:\Sopen a menu with various list options.|MChoose one of the menu items to make a list of the selected text.
HlpSmilies:\Sopen a palette of different smilies.|MChoose one of the icons to insert a smiley into the text.

# Syntax colouring groups
Group1:Bold
Group2:Italic
Group3:Underline
Group4:Email
Group5:Code
Group6:URL
Group7:Img
Group8:Color
Group9:Size
Group10:Lists
